-- AIG says Peter Hancock to replace Robert Benmosche as CEO
-- By Avik Das in Bangalore
-- Tue Jun 10, 2014 04:22PM EDT
-- None



June 10 (Reuters) - American International Group Inc <AIG.N> said it named Peter Hancock as its new chief executive, effective Sept. 1.

Hancock, the head of the insurer's global property-casualty business, succeeds Robert Benmosche, who will retire in September. [ID:nBwQG4Zza]